A short comic series with @ginzamagazine
" My 80-year-old grandma "
EP4: The Hug

The story is about an 80-year-old grandmother, teenage grandson, and a family full of generation gaps.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by SUNDAE KIDS on July 26, 2021 tagging @sundaekids. May be a cartoon of text.

Photo by SUNDAE KIDS on July 26, 2021. May be a cartoon of 4 people and text that says 'DON'T FORGET YOUR LUNCH. お弁当を忘れないでね。 DID YOU FINISH YOUR HOMEWORK? 宿題は終わったの？ আনর WHAT TIME WILL YOU RETURN HOME? 何時に帰ってくる？ GRANDMA.. おばあちゃん YOU DON'T HAVE TO WALK ME TO SCHOOL. 緒に学校まで歩 かなくてもいいよ！ COME ON! IT'S FUN. いいじゃない！ 楽しいんだし。 HAVEN'T WALKED YOU TO SCHOOL SINCE YOU WERE KID. 子供の時以来学校まで 緒に歩いてないのよ？'.
